name: Progetto Regró
description: This is an interactive svg for Regró (https://serestelitano.wixsite.com/regro) which shows day/night cycles , a tree's respiration cycle, and localized seasons like Winter and Summer in some regions/timezones like Europe(London,Berlin,Rome, Moscow), America(Los Angeles, Saō Paulo), Asia(Calcutta, Shanghai, Tokyo), Africa(Nairobi, Johannesburg), Australia, and New Zealand. More locations will be added over time.
